name: Moss Events
tag_list: events, event-coordination, event-marketing, corporate-events, private-events, promotions, event-promotions, branding, sponsorship
overview: Moss Events is a full service event management company. From all-inclusive event production to simple venue negotiations, Moss Events has years of experience and the kind of expertise required to ensure that each guest walks away from the event thoroughly impressed. The synergy of Moss Events with the Moss Marketing and Moss Public Relations divisions provide insight not only into the production details of each event, but also the promotion and marketing value of it. With Moss Events, productions include corporate events, networking mixers, movie premiers, store openings, tradeshows and conferences. The mission of Moss Events is to produce events that make an immediate, profound impression.
